              <td width="593" height="57" align="left" valign="top"><h1 class="titleh1">New College Loan Reimbursement Program Funded by New York City Police Foundation to Bolster Ranks of NYPD</h1></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td width="593" height="699" align="left" valign="top"><table width="624" height="547" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
